You can use `BeforeEach` annotation within Junit class:


    @BeforeEach
    void foo() {
        clearDBrows();
    }

    void clearDBrows(){
    //clear db rows 
    ..
    }

This is by considering, your other test&#39;s wont really care if db table rows get cleared before execution as `@BeforeEach` will get executed for every tests you run.

